### 2. Role-Permission Management

Create admin UI:

```text
/settings/roles
/settings/roles/{id}/permissions
```

Allow admin to:

* view roles
* assign permissions to roles
* remove permissions from roles

---

### 3. Permission Helper / Service

Create reusable helper or service:

```php
user_can('works.create')
user_can_any(['works.update', 'works.delete'])
user_can_all(['cases.view', 'cases.status_update'])
```

---

### 4. Route Protection

Protect routes by permission, not only login.

Examples:

```text
/works/create → works.create
/licenses → licenses.view
/cases/{id}/status → cases.status_update
/activities → activities.view
/settings/roles → settings.manage
```

---

### 5. UI Permission Control

Hide or disable buttons when user lacks permission:

```text
Create Work
Edit
Delete
Create License
Change Case Status
Manage Roles
```

---

### 6. Seeder

Create default permissions and assign:

```text
admin → all permissions
manager → view/create/update for works, owners, licenses, usage reports, cases
viewer → view-only permissions
```

---

### 7. Audit Logging

Log role/permission changes:

```text
PERMISSION_ASSIGNED
PERMISSION_REMOVED
ROLE_UPDATED
```

